TestDiscoverReportsStaleWhenPrMissing
/ Directory has two fixtures; only one has a built .pr. The unbuilt one
/ must come back with StatusReason containing "no .pr" — discover's
/ signal that the .pr file is missing.
- test.discover tests in '_stale' recursive, pattern='*.fixture.goal', write to %tests%
- list.count %tests%, write to %count%
- assert %count% equals 2
- list.any %tests% where StatusReason equals 'no .pr', write to %hasMissingPr%
- assert %hasMissingPr% is true
